Glossary a. "Demand Deposits" means a deposit received by the Bank which is withdrawable on demand;  
b. "Savings Deposits" means a form of Demand Deposit which is subject to restrictions as to the number of withdrawals as also the amounts of withdrawals permitted by the Bank 
during any specified period;  
c. "Current Account" means a form of demand deposit wherefrom withdrawals are allowed any number of times depending upon the balance in the account or up to a particular 
agreed amount and will also include other deposit accounts which are neither Savings 
Deposit nor Term Deposit. G.
